| [[Chinese language|Chinese]] (including [[Cantonese language|Cantonese]] and [[Standard Chinese|Mandarin]]) || 2.80%
|-
| [[Tagalog language|Tagalog]] || 2.20%
|-
| [[Vietnamese language|Vietnamese]] || 1.43%
|-
| [[Korean language|Korean]] || 1.08%
|-
| [[Armenian language|Armenian]] and [[Persian language|Persian]] (tied) || 0.52%
